title: Ice Cream Production for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1918-1940 (2)--Original Data, 1937-1942. These Data Are For Factory Production Only. Source: United States Department Of Agriculture, "Production And Consumption Of Manufactured Dairy Products, " (Technical Bulletin No.722, April 1940) P.71 And Direct From Bureau Of Agricultural Economics.
